==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sock in
<hw>Sock in</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>to cause (an
airport) to cease functioning, by severe weather conditions, such as fog
or a snowstorm. Used often in the passive; <as>the airport was
<ex>socked in</ex> for two days by a blizzard</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sockdolager</ent>⟦br⟧
